c', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/169787/', '', 'Cyclophosphamide, Streptozocin, Chlorambucil, Melphalan, Mechlorethamine, Ifosfamide, Melphalan flufenamide', 'Entrectinib, Pralsetinib, Dabrafenib, Asciminib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Pacritinib, Tepotinib, Fedratinib, Avapritinib, Larotrectinib, More', 1767369485);
